{"tid":2415132,"cid":15,"subCid":0,"title":"9988 阿里巴巴一個月內升到$320破頂集氣區","createTime":"2021-02-20T04:14:52.000Z","updateTime":"2021-02-23T07:16:11.000Z","uid":215603,"like":11,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":30,"replies":[{"pid":"78f33792afb33636154b9d78ea9bd22c09b39e3a","tid":2415132,"uid":215603,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-20T04:14:52.000Z","msg":"9988 阿里巴巴一個月內升到$320破頂集氣區<br />\n理據:<br />\n第三財季淨利潤按年增長52%至794.27億人民幣 勝預期<br />\nARK買入大量阿里巴巴股份<br />\n耀才證券(<a href=\"http://01428.HK\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2F01428.HK&d=8a%2F9oMJQTUqWgqWpHd%2BbkhphPZUtdHSu9roW7Om9%2Fes%3D&h=df40196a\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">01428.HK</a>)斥1.87億購阿里巴巴(<a href=\"http://09988.HK\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2F09988.HK&d=8a%2F9oMJQTUqWgqWpHd%2BbkhphPZUtdHSu9roW7Om9%2Fes%3D&h=a3a42b7d\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">09988.HK</a>)近77萬股<br />\n阿里(<a href=\"http://09988.HK\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2F09988.HK&d=8a%2F9oMJQTUqWgqWpHd%2BbkhphPZUtdHSu9roW7Om9%2Fes%3D&h=a3a42b7d\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">09988.HK</a>)將股份回購額度提升至100億美元<br />\n據報螞蟻與中國監管機構就重組計劃達成協議<br />\n花旗上調阿里巴巴(<a href=\"http://09988.HK\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2F09988.HK&d=8a%2F9oMJQTUqWgqWpHd%2BbkhphPZUtdHSu9roW7Om9%2Fes%3D&h=a3a42b7d\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">09988.HK</a>)目標價至334元 維持「買入」評級<br />\n德銀升阿里巴巴(<a href=\"http://09988.HK\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2F09988.HK&d=8a%2F9oMJQTUqWgqWpHd%2BbkhphPZUtdHSu9roW7Om9%2Fes%3D&h=a3a42b7d\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">09988.HK</a>)目標價至318元"},{"pid":"3a4131fca0048830cd5a50680fb827930b33667d","tid":2415132,"uid":133946,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-20T04:15:27.000Z","msg":"人唔笑<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"77be2c592f062d819f1235a6cc282a631925e693","tid":2415132,"uid":8410,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"reply